\id 1JN JN - Zanaki 1 John
\h 1 Yohana
\toc3 1 Yohana
\toc2 1 Yohana
\toc1 Enyaarubha yo okutaanga ya Yohana
\mt2 Enyaarubha yo okutaanga ya
\mt1 Yohana
\imt1 Obhutaangiro
\ip Enyaarubha yino ekakaamwa na Yohana. Muziinyaarubha isatu zya Yohana, hano akubhuga “etwe,” ariitogora omweene hamwe na abheega abharikyaaye. Hano Yohana yaakaamiri eziinyaarubha zino, yaari akuunguhiri. Munyaarubha yino, Yohana akakaamira Abhakrisito bhano yabhaseegiri bhukongʼu. Akabhabhirikira “abhaana bhaane abhaseegwa.”
\ip Yohana arabheegya Abhakrisito kubha, Taatabhugya ni bhweero, na abhaatu bhano bhakumwiikirirya bhareenderwa kwiikara mubhweero. Omuutu wuno akumwiikirirya Taatabhugya atakutura kwiikara mubhibhi. Yohana arabhatoongera iguru yo obhwiikari bhwe Ekikrisito. Taatabhugya ni bhuseegi nikyo abhaatu bhaaye bhareenderwa okuseegana. Okumuseega Taatabhugya no okumuseega omurikyaaye ni kigiro kimwe. Kweeki arabharekya iguru ya ameegyo go orurimi. Haari na abheegya abharebhe bhano bhaari bhatigiri amakanisa gaabhu, bhakabha bhariiruguura ahagiro hayo no okuraarika ameegyo go orurimi. Kukira gayo, Yohana arakumiirirya obhuheene bhwo obhwiikirirya bhwe Ekikrisito, okubha abhagumirye no okubhagosorerya abhaatu mubhwiikirirya. Mumeegyo gaaye arakeerenerya iguru yo obhuseegi, okwaabhirana, obhwiigwaani, okuhiza ebhibhi, okwiikara obhwiikari bhuno bhukumuzomera Taatabhugya, na iguru yo obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego.
\c 1
\s1 Engʼana yo obhuhoru
\p 
\v 1 Turabharaarika amangʼana iguru ye Engʼana yo obhuhoru, Engʼana wuyo yaari ariho okurwa obhweemero.\f + \fr 1:1 \xt Rora Obhweemero 1:1; Yohana 1:1-3.\xt*\f* Etwe tukamwiigwa no okumurora kwa ameeso geetu, tukamwiisuunza no okumubhabhaata na amabhoko geetu.
\v 2 Obhuhoru bhuyo bhukarorekana, na neetwe tukabhurora. Bhoono, turabhamenyeekererya no okubharwaazira amangʼana iguru ya wuno ni Ngʼana yo obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego. Ewe yaari ku Taata Taatabhugya, akarorekana kweetwe.\f + \fr 1:2 \xt Rora Yohana 1:14.\xt*\f*
\v 3 Tukamurora no okumwiigwa, na bhoono turabharwaazira amangʼana iguru waaye, okubha mubhe no obhumwe neetwe mubhwiikirirya. Obhumwe bhuno tunabhwe hamwe na Taata Taatabhugya, no Omwaana waaye\f + \fr 1:3 \fk Omwaana waaye\ft . Rora \ft \it Omwaana wa Taatabhugya\it* mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* Yeesu Krisito.
\v 4 Turabhakaamira gano, okubha obhuzomererwa bhweetu bhuhike.
\s1 Okwiikara mubhweero
\p 
\v 5 Ambe, amangʼana gano tukiigwa okurwa ku Krisito Yeesu, nigo tukubharwaazira, kubha Taatabhugya ni bhweero, atana kiirima kyokyoosi muusi waaye.
\v 6 Eraabhe turabhuga tuno obhumwe na Taatabhugya, eno turageenderera kwiikara mukiirima, turagaamba orurimi, na tutakukora go obhuheene.
\v 7 Nawe, eraabhe turiikara mubhweero, kyeego Taatabhugya ari mubhweero, niho tuno obhumwe etwe abheene kwa abheene. Kweeki amanyiinga go Omwaana waaye Yeesu garatweerya ebhibhi bhyeetu bhyoosi.
\p 
\v 8 Eraabhe turabhuga kubha etwe tutana ebhibhi bhyobhyoosi, turiingʼeena abheene, naabhe obhuheene bhutari muusi weetu.
\v 9 Nawe, eraabhe turiisasaama ebhibhi bhyeetu, Taatabhugya aratwaabhira ebhibhi bhyeetu no okutweerya obhubhi bhwoosi, kwo okubha ewe ni muheene na mweene heene.
\v 10 Eraabhe turabhuga kubha tukyaari kukora ebhibhi, turamukora Taatabhugya kubha mubheehi, naabhe engʼana yaaye etari muusi weetu.
\c 2
\s1 Yeesu Krisito niwe akutusabhira
\p 
\v 1 Abhaana bhaane abhaseegwa, nirabhakaamira amangʼana gayo, okubha mutakora ebhibhi. Nawe, kyo omuutu wowoosi arikora ebhibhi, tunawe wuno akutwiimeererera ku Taata Taatabhugya. Wuyo niwe Yeesu Krisito omuheene.
\v 2 Ewe niwe ekimweeso kyo okuruusyaho ebhibhi bhyeetu no okutwiigwaania na Taatabhugya. Kweeki, etari ebhibhi bhyeetu ebhyeene, nawe ni bhibhi bhya abhaatu bhoosi bhe ekyaaro.
\p 
\v 3 Turaagwaate obhuswaagyo bhwa Taatabhugya, niho tukumenya kubha turamumenyeekererya.
\v 4 Wowoosi wuno akubhuga kubha, amumenyiri Taatabhugya eno atakwiigwa obhuswaagyo bhwaaye, ni mubheehi, naabhe obhuheene bhutari muusi waaye.
\v 5 Nawe omuutu wuno akwiigwa engʼana yaaye, eheene obhuseegi bhwa Taatabhugya bhukuunaaniri muusi waaye. Kweego turamenya kubha tuno obhumwe na Taatabhugya.
\v 6 Omuutu wuno akubhuga ano obhumwe na Taatabhugya, areenderwa yiikare kyeego Yeesu akiikara.
\s1 Obhuswaagyo bhwa Yeesu iguru yo okuseegana
\p 
\v 7 Abhaseegwa bhaane, obhuswaagyo bhuno nikubhakaamira bhutari bhuhya, nawe ni bhuswaagyo bhuryabhurya bhwe ekare bhuno mwaari mumenyiri kweema hano mwaataangiri okwiikirirya Yeesu Krisito.\f + \fr 2:7 \xt Rora Yohana 13:34.\xt*\f* Obhuswaagyo bhuyo bhwe ekare, ni ngʼana yirya yino mukiigwa iguru yo okuseegana.
\v 8 Kweeki, obhuswaagyo bhuno nikubhakaamira, nibhwo obhuhya. Obhuheene bhwo obhuswaagyo bhuyo, bhukarorekana mubhwiikari bhwa Yeesu Krisito na mubhwiikari bhweenyu, bhuno bhukutweerekya kubha ekiirima kirarwaho no obhweero bhwe eheene bhumariri kubhara.
\p 
\v 9 Omuutu wowoosi wuno akubhuga, ariikara mubhweero eno aramubhiihirirya omurikyaaye, akyaari ariikara mukiirima.
\v 10 Wuyo woosi wuno akuseega omurikyaaye, ariikara mubhweero. Kitariho kyokyoosi muusi waaye kyo okumugirirya akore ebhibhi.
\v 11 Nawe, wuno akumubhiihirirya omurikyaaye, ari mukiirima. Kweeki, arageenda mukiirima, atakumenya eno akugya, kwo okubha ekiirima kikuundikiirye ameeso gaaye.
\q1 
\v 12 Nirabhakaamira abhaana bhaane abhaseegwa,
\q1 kwo okubha ebhibhi bhyeenyu bhyaabhiirwe // kwo okuhitira Yeesu Krisito.
\q1 
\v 13 Nirabhakaamira emwe bhataata,
\q1 kwo okubha mumumenyiri Yeesu Krisito,
\q1 wuno yaariho kweema obhweemero.
\q1 Nirabhakaamira emwe abhamura,
\q1 kwo okubha mumuhiziri Seetaani, omubhi wurya.
\q1 Nirabhakaamira emwe abhaana,
\q1 kwo okubha mumumenyiri Taata Taatabhugya.
\q1 
\v 14 Nirabhakaamira emwe bhataata,
\q1 kwo okubha mumumenyiri Yeesu Krisito,
\q1 wuno yaariho kweema obhweemero.
\q1 Nirabhakaamira emwe abhamura,
\q1 kwo okubha muna amanaga,
\q1 murageenderera okugwaata eriingʼana rya Taatabhugya,
\q1 kweeki, mumuhiziri Seetaani, omubhi wurya.
\p 
\v 15 Kweego, mutaseega obhubhi bhwe ekyaaro kino na goosi gano garimu. Omuutu wowoosi hano akuseega amangʼana ga mukyaaro, atakumuseega Taata Taatabhugya.
\v 16 Obhubhi bhwe ekyaaro nibhwo bhuno, enaamba embiihu yo omubhiri, enaamba yo okubha nakyo kyokyoosi kino omuutu akiruuzi, no obhwiizuungya bhuno bhukutuukana no obhuniibhi. Eziiteemwa ziyo zitakureka ku Taata Taatabhugya, nawe zirareka mukyaaro muno.
\v 17 Ekyaaro kino hamwe ne eziinaamba zyakyo eziimbiihu, zirahita. Nawe wowoosi wuno akukora gano gakumuzomera Taatabhugya, arabha no obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego.
\s1 Mwiiriihe na abhabhisa bha Krisito
\p 
\v 18 Abhaana bhaane abhaseegwa, eziisiku zyo obhuteero zihikiri! Mwiigwiiri kubha omwaangi wa Krisito\f + \fr 2:18 \fk Omwaangi wa Krisito\ft , obhugazuro bhwaku ni \fqa wuno akumwaanga Krisito.\f* araaza, naabhe bhoono abhaangi bhaaru bha Krisito bhamariri kuuza. Ego niigo tumenyiri kubha turi muziisiku zyo obhuteero.
\v 19 Abhaatu bhayo bharwiiri gati weetu, nawe bhataari no obhumwe bhwe eheene na neetwe. Eraabhe bhiingabheeri no obhumwe bhwe eheene na neetwe, bhiingatamiri kweetwe. Nawe bhakatanura, okubha emenyekane kubhoosi kubha bhataari no obhumwe neetwe.
\p 
\v 20 Nawe emwe, Omuhoreeru Yeesu abhaheeri Ekoro yaaye,\f + \fr 2:20 \fk Abhaheeri Ekoro yaaye\ft , ku Kiyunaani ni, \fqa muhakirwe amaguta. \ft Eriibhaga rye Eriiragano rye Ekare, Abhiiziraeri bhaari bharatuura abhaatu mumirimo gya abhaseengeri na gyo obhutemi. Akabhahaka amaguta mumitwe okweerekya kubha Taatabhugya abhaheeri emirimo emirebhe hamwe no obhunagya bhwe Ekoro Muhoreeru. Rora \ft \it Ekoro Muhoreeru\it* mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu. \xt Rora 1 Samweeri 16:13; Isaya 61:1.\xt*\f* bhoono emwe mwoosi mumenyiri obhuheene.
\v 21 Nirabhakaamira enyaarubha yino, etari kwo okubha mutamenyiri obhuheene, nawe mubhumenyiri. Kweeki, mumenyiri kubha rutariho orurimi rworwoosi runo rukutuukana no obhuheene.
\v 22 Omuutu omubheehi ni weewi? Omuutu omubheehi ni wowoosi wuno akugaamba kubha Yeesu atari Krisito.\f + \fr 2:22 \fk Krisito \ft ni ngʼana ye Ekiyunaani, obhugazuro bhwaku ni \fqa wuno ahakirwe amaguta. \ft Mu Kieburania bharabhuga \fqa Masiya. \ft Rora engʼana yino mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* Wowoosi wuno akwaanga Taata Taatabhugya na Yeesu Omwaana waaye, niwe omwaangi wa Krisito.
\v 23 Omuutu wowoosi wuno akumwaanga Omwaana wa Taatabhugya, atana obhumwe na Taata Taatabhugya. Nawe, wuno akumwiisasaama Omwaana embere wa abhaatu, ano obhumwe na Taata Taatabhugya kweeki.
\p 
\v 24 Bhoono, mugeenderere okugagwaata muziikoro zyeenyu amangʼana gano mweegiibhwe go okumwiikirirya Yeesu, kweema obhweemero. Eraabhe murageenderera okugwaata ameegyo gayo, niho murageenderera kubha no obhumwe no Omwaana na Taata Taatabhugya
\v 25 na bhuno nibhwo obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego bhuno akaturagania.
\p 
\v 26 Nirabhakaamira amangʼana gayo, okubharekya iguru wa abhaatu bhano bhakusakya okubhabhurya.
\v 27 Nawe emwe, Krisito abhaheeri Ekoro Muhoreeru, wuno akwiikara muusi weenyu. Wuyo niwe akubheegya goosi, na ameegyo gaaye ni ge eheene, gatari go orurimi. Kweego, mutakweenderwa okweegibhwa no owuundi.\f + \fr 2:27 \xt Rora Yohana 14:26.\xt*\f* Kyeego Ekoro Muhoreeru abheegirye, mugeenderere kubha no obhumwe na Krisito.
\p 
\v 28 Bhoono abhaana bhaane abhaseegwa, mugeenderere kubha no obhumwe na Krisito, okubha eriibhaga rino araakyoore kweeki, tubhe no obhukaari embere waaye, tutiibhisa kwe eziisoni.
\p 
\v 29 Mumenyiri kubha Krisito ni mweene heene. Kweego mumenye kubha wowoosi wuno akukora ge eheene, niwe omwaana wa Taatabhugya.
\c 3
\s1 Okwiikara kya abhaana bha Taatabhugya
\p 
\v 1 Murore kyeego Taata Taatabhugya akutuseega bhukongʼu, kubha etwe tubhirikiirwe abhaana bhaaye! Eheene niigo turi. Nawe abhaatu bhano bhatakumwiigwa Taatabhugya, bhatakumenyeekererya kubha etwe ni bhaana bha Taatabhugya, kwo okubha bhatamumenyiri ewe.
\v 2 Abhaseegwa bhaane, tumenyiri kubha bhoono ego etwe ni bhaana bha Taatabhugya, nawe etamenyekeeni kyaabhurya turaabhe. Nawe tumenyiri kubha eriibhaga rino Krisito araakyoore kweeki, turatuubhana neewe, kwo okubha turamurora kyeego ari.
\v 3 Omuutu wowoosi wuno akwiisiga kubha aratuubhana na Krisito, yiyeerye okubha abhe muhoreeru, kyeego Krisito omweene ni muhoreeru.
\p 
\v 4 Wowoosi wuno akukora ebhibhi, arasarya emigiro gya Taatabhugya, kwo okubha okukora ebhibhi, nikwo okusarya emigiro.
\v 5 Mumenyiri kubha Krisito akaaza mukyaaro, okubha abhiruusyeho ebhibhi bhyeetu. Kweeki ewe atana bhibhi bhyobhyoosi muusi waaye.
\v 6 Bhoono eri mwaasi kubha, wowoosi wuno akugeenderera kubha no obhumwe neewe, atakugeenderera kukora ebhibhi. Nawe wowoosi wuno akugeenderera kukora ebhibhi, akyaari kumurora, naabhe atamumenyiri Krisito ni weewi.
\p 
\v 7 Bhoono, abhaana bhaane abhaseegwa, mutiikirirya kubha omuutu wowoosi abhabhurye. Wowoosi wuno akukora amangʼana ge eheene, ni muheene embere wa Taatabhugya, kyeego Krisito ni we eheene.
\v 8 Nawe wowoosi wuno akugeenderera kukora ebhibhi, ni muutu wa Seetaani.\f + \fr 3:8 \fk Seetaani\ft . Rora engʼana yino mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* Tumenyiri ego, kwo okubha Seetaani ageendereeri kukora ebhibhi kweema obhweemero. Nikyo ekigirirye Omwaana wa Taatabhugya akaaza mukyaaro, okubha agisarye emirimo gya Seetaani.
\p 
\v 9 Wowoosi wuno abheeri omwaana wa Taatabhugya, atakugeenderera kukora ebhibhi, kwo okubha ano obhuhoru okurwa ku Taatabhugya. Atakunagya kugeenderera kukora ebhibhi, kwo okubha ni mwaana wa Taatabhugya.
\v 10 Nawe, omuutu wuno atakukora amangʼana ge eheene kasi wuno atakumuseega omurikyaaye, wuyo atari omwaana wa Taatabhugya. Gayo nigo gakwaahura gati wa abhaana bha Taatabhugya na abhaana bha Seetaani.
\s1 Museegane
\p 
\v 11 Kweema eriibhaga hano mwaataangiri okwiikirirya, mwiigwiiri amangʼana kubha tureenderwa okuseegana etwe kwe etwe.
\v 12 Tutabha kya Kaini, omwaana wa Seetaani, omubhi wurya, wuno akiita omusuuhu waaye.\f + \fr 3:12 \xt Rora Obhweemero 4:1-8.\xt*\f* Ni kwaki akamwiita? Akamwiita kwo okubha amahokya gaaye Kaini gaari mabhiihu, nawe go omusuuhu waaye gaari ge eheene.
\p 
\v 13 Kweego abharikyaane, mutaruguura eraabhe abhaatu bhano bhatakumwiigwa Taatabhugya bharabhiihirirwa.
\v 14 Etwe tumenyiri kubha tuhoniri oruku, na bhoono tuno obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego. Tumenyiri ego, kwo okubha tubhaseegiri abharikyeetu. Omuutu wowoosi wuno atana obhuseegi, akyaari kuhona oruku.\f + \fr 3:14 \xt Rora Yohana 5:24.\xt*\f*
\v 15 Wowoosi wuno amubhiihiriirye omurikyaaye, ni mwiiti. Mumenyiri kubha atariho omwiiti wuno ano obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego muusi waaye.
\p 
\v 16 Krisito, hano yaruusirye obhwiikari bhwaaye kwiiguru weetu, akatweerekya obhuseegi bhwe eheene. Kweeki na neetwe egoego, tureenderwa okuruusya obhwiikari bhweetu kwiiguru ya abharikyeetu.
\v 17 Omuutu wowoosi we ebhigiro bhyo okwiisa, arimurora omurikyaaye ano obhweendi, nawe atana ebhigoongi bhyo okumusakirya, eheene ano obhuseegi bhwa Taatabhugya?
\p 
\v 18 Abhaana bhaane abhaseegwa mubhwiikirirya, tutaseegana kwa amangʼana ageene, nawe tuseegane kwe eheene no okukorerana amazomu.
\v 19 Turiseegana ego, niho tukubha abhaatu bhe eheene kubha turatuniirira obhuheene, kweeki eziikoro zyeetu zirahiinyika embere wa Taatabhugya.
\v 20 Naabhe turitinirwa ekiina muziikoro zyeetu, kubha tukoriri ebhibhi, tumenyiri kubha Taatabhugya niwe Omukuru kukira eziikoro zyeetu, neewe amenyiri goosi.
\p 
\v 21 Abhaseegwa bhaane, eraabhe tutakutinirwa ekiina muziikoro zyeetu, turanagya kubha no obhukaari bhwo okusabha embere wa Taatabhugya.
\v 22 Kweeki turasuungʼaana okurwa kweewe ryoryoosi rino tukumusabha, kwo okubha tugwaatiri obhuswaagyo bhwaaye no okukora gano gakumuzomera.
\p 
\v 23 Obhuswaagyo bhwaaye nibhwe bhuno, kubha twiikirirye eriina ryo Omwaana waaye, Yeesu Krisito no okuseegana, kyeego akaturagania.
\v 24 Omuutu wowoosi wuno akwiigwa obhuswaagyo bhwa Taatabhugya, ano obhumwe neewe. Taatabhugya kweeki ano obhumwe neewe. Tumenyiri kubha Taatabhugya ariikara mubhumwe neetwe, kwo okubha tune Ekoro Muhoreeru wuno atuheeri.
\c 4
\s1 Okumenya ekoro ye eheene ne ekoro yo orurimi
\p 
\v 1 Abhaseegwa bhaane, mutiikirirya omuutu wowoosi wuno akubhuga ane Ekoro Muhoreeru wa Taatabhugya. Nawe mwiisuunze bhuzomu eraabhe omuutu arakaangatwa ne Ekoro Muhoreeru wa Taatabhugya kasi zeyi. Ni kuzomu okumenyeekererya kisi ego, kwo okubha abharooti bhaaru bho orurimi bhari mukyaaro.
\v 2 Enzira yo okumumenya omuutu wuno akukaangatwa ne Ekoro Muhoreeru wa Taatabhugya niyo yino: wowoosi wuno akwiikirirya kubha Yeesu Krisito akaaza mukyaaro no omubhiri gwo omuutu, wuyo niwe akukaangatwa ne Ekoro wa Taatabhugya.
\v 3 Nawe wowoosi wuno atakwiikirirya kubha Yeesu yaari no omubhiri gwo omuutu, atakukaangatwa ne Ekoro wa Taatabhugya. Omuutu wuyo arakaangatwa ne ekoro yo omwaangi wa Krisito. Neemwe, mwiigwiiri kubha ekoro yo omwaangi wuyo eraaza, na bhoono emariri kuuza mukyaaro.
\p 
\v 4 Nawe, abhaana bhaane abhaseegwa mubhwiikirirya, emwe ni bhaana bha Taatabhugya, neemwe muhiziri abharooti bhayo bho orurimi. Mukanagya okubhahiza kwo okubha Ekoro ya Taatabhugya eri muusi weenyu. Ewe ano obhunagya kukira ekoro ya Seetaani wuno ari mukyaaro.
\v 5 Abharooti bhayo bho orurimi ni bha mukyaaro, kweego bharagaamba amangʼana ge ekyaaro. Na abhaatu bha mukyaaro bhano bhatakumwiigwa Taatabhugya, bharabhiitegeerera.
\v 6 Etwe ni bhaana bha Taatabhugya. Wowoosi wuno amumenyiri Taatabhugya, aratwiigwa. Nawe wuno atari omwaana wa Taatabhugya, atakutwiigwa. Ego niigo tumenyiri obhwaahuri gati wa abhaatu bhano bhakukaangatibhwa ne Ekoro we eheene, na bhano bhakukaangatibhwa ne ekoro yo orurimi.
\s1 Taatabhugya ni bhuseegi
\p 
\v 7 Abhaseegwa bhaane, tuseegane, kwo okubha obhuseegi bhurarwa ku Taatabhugya. Omuutu wowoosi wuno akuseega abharikyaaye, ni mwaana wa Taatabhugya, kweeki niwe amumenyiri Taatabhugya.
\v 8 Nawe, wowoosi wuno atakuseega abharikyaaye, atamumenyiri Taatabhugya, kwo okubha Taatabhugya ni bhuseegi.
\p 
\v 9 Taatabhugya akeerekya obhuseegi bhwaaye kweetwe, kwe enzira yo okuragania Omwaana waaye omweene mukyaaro, okubha kuhitira kweewe tubhone obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego.
\v 10 Bhuno nibhwo obhuseegi, etari kubha etwe tukamuseega Taatabhugya, nawe ewe niwe akatuseega etwe. Nikyo akaragania Omwaana waaye, okubha abhe ekimweeso kyo okuruusyaho ebhibhi bhyeetu no okutugwaatania na Taatabhugya.
\v 11 Abhaseegwa bhaane, kwo okubha Taatabhugya akatuseega etwe, ereenderwa na neetwe twiiseege.
\v 12 Atariho omuutu wowoosi wuno amuruuzi Taatabhugya kimwe. Nawe turiiseege, Taatabhugya ariikara mubhumwe na neetwe, no obhuseegi bhwaaye bhurakuunaana muusi weetu.
\p 
\v 13 Etwe tuno obhumwe na Taatabhugya, neewe Taatabhugya ano obhumwe na neetwe. Tumenyiri ego, kwo okubha atuheeri Ekoro yaaye.
\v 14 Etwe tumuruuzi no okubhamenyeekererya abhaandi kubha Taata Taatabhugya akamutuma mukyaaro omwaana waaye, okubha abhe Omutuurya wa abhaatu bhoosi.
\v 15 Omuutu wowoosi wuno akwiikirirya kubha Yeesu ni Mwaana wa Taatabhugya, Taatabhugya arabha no obhumwe neewe, neewe arabha no obhumwe na Taatabhugya.
\v 16 Bhoono, etwe tumenyiri no okwiikirirya kubha Taatabhugya aratuseega. Taatabhugya ni bhuseegi. Wowoosi wuno akwiikara kwo obhuseegi, niwe ano obhumwe na Taatabhugya, Taatabhugya woosi ano obhumwe neewe.
\p 
\v 17 Kwe enzira yiyo, obhuseegi bhukuunaaniri muusi weetu, okubha tubhe no obhukaari kurusiku rwo okutinirwa ekiina. Obhuseegi bhuyo bhukuunaaniri, kwo okubha obhwiikari bhweetu mukyaaro muno, bhuratuubhana na kyeego Yeesu akiikara.
\v 18 Omuutu wuno ano obhuseegi, atana ehaho, kwo okubha obhuseegi bhwe eheene bhuraruusya ehaho yoosi. Omuutu ane haho hano okwoobhoha obhutini bhwe ekiina. Omuutu wuno ane ehaho, obhuseegi bhukyaari kukuunaana muusi waaye.
\p 
\v 19 Etwe turamuseega Taatabhugya na abharikyeetu kwo okubha Taatabhugya niwe akakaangata kutuseega etwe.
\v 20 Eraabhe omuutu wowoosi arabhuga kubha aramuseega Taatabhugya, eno aramubhiihirirya omurikyaaye, ni mubheehi. Tumenyiri kubha ni mubheehi, kwo okubha aribha atakumuseega omurikyaaye wuno akumurora kwa ameeso, atakunagya kumuseega Taatabhugya wuno akyaari kumurora.
\v 21 Ambe, Taatabhugya atuheeri obhuswaagyo bhuno kubha, wowoosi wuno akumuseega Taatabhugya, areenderwa amuseege omurikyaaye.\f + \fr 4:21 \xt Rora Abharaawi 19:18; Obhuhiiti bhwe Emigiro 6:4-5; Mariko 12:30-31.\xt*\f*
\c 5
\s1 Obhwiikirirya bhuhiziri ebhibhi bhye ekyaaro
\p 
\v 1 Omuutu wowoosi wuno akwiikirirya kubha Yeesu ni Krisito, wuyo niwe omwaana wa Taatabhugya. Wowoosi wuno akumuseega taata, arabhaseega naabhe abhaana bha taata wuyo.
\v 2 Tumenyiri kubha, turabhaseega abhaana bha Taatabhugya kwe enzira yo okumuseega Taatabhugya, no okugwaata obhuswaagyo bhwaaye.
\v 3 Okumuseega Taatabhugya nikwe okugwaata obhuswaagyo bhwaaye. Kweeki, okugwaata obhuswaagyo bhwaaye kutari kukongʼu,
\v 4 kwo okubha abhaana bhoosi bha Taatabhugya bharahiza obhubhi bhwe ekyaaro. Kuno nikwo okuhiza ekyaaro kwo obhwiikirirya bhweetu.
\v 5 Awee, ni weewi wuno akunagya okuhiza obhubhi bhwe ekyaaro? Ni wuno akwiikirirya kubha Yeesu ni Mwaana wa Taatabhugya.
\s1 Obhumenyeekererya iguru wa Yeesu Krisito
\p 
\v 6 Yeesu Krisito niwe akakuundukurirwa kubha omwaana wa Taatabhugya kwa amaanzi go obhubatiizo bhwaaye na amanyiinga gaaye gano gakiitika kumusaraba. Ateerekirye ego kwo okubatiizwa kwa amaanzi ageene, nawe kwo okwiitira amanyiinga gaaye kumusaraba.
\v 7 Kweeki neewe Ekoro Muhoreeru niwe wuno akumenyeekererya kubha ni ge eheene, kwo okubha Ekoro Muhoreeru niwe obhuheene.
\v 8 Mbe, bhariho abhamenyeekererya bhatatu, bhano bhakweerekya amangʼana ga Yeesu [mwiisaaro, ni Taata, Engʼana ne Ekoro Muhoreeru, na abhatatu bhano ni bhamwe.
\v 9 Kweeki, bhiriho bhitatu bhino bhikumenyeekererya mukyaaro], nabhyo ni Koro, amaanzi na amanyiinga, ne ebhitatu bhiyo bhiriikirirania. Eraabhe turiikirirya obhumenyeekererya bhwa abhaatu, eheene turanagya okwiikirirya obhumenyeekererya obhukuru bhuno Taatabhugya akaruusya iguru yo Omwaana waaye.
\p 
\v 10 Wowoosi wuno akumwiikirirya Omwaana wa Taatabhugya, yiikirirye kubha obhumenyeekererya bhuyo ni bhwe eheene. Nawe wuno atakwiikirirya amangʼana ga Taatabhugya, arabhuga Taatabhugya ni mubheehi, kwo okubha akyaari kubhwiikirirya obhumenyeekererya bhuno Taatabhugya aruusirye iguru yo Omwaana waaye.
\v 11 Obhumenyeekererya bhuyo nibhwo bhuno, Taatabhugya atuheeri obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego. Obhuhoru bhuyo, tubhweeni kwe enzira yo okwiikirirya Omwaana waaye.
\v 12 Wowoosi wuno akubha no obhumwe no Omwaana wa Taatabhugya, anabhwo obhuhoru. Nawe wuno atana obhumwe no Omwaana wa Taatabhugya, atana obhuhoru.
\s1 Orubhaango rwo obhwiikari bhwa kirakeego
\p 
\v 13 Nibhakaamiiri amangʼana gayo, bhano mukwiikirirya eriina ryo Omwaana wa Taatabhugya, okubha mumenye kubha muno obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego.
\v 14 Etwe tuno obhukaari bhukuru embere wa Taatabhugya, kwo okubha tumenyiri aratwiigwa hano tukumusabha ryoryoosi kutuukana no obhuseegi bhwaaye.
\v 15 Tumenyiri kubha aratwiitegeerera hano tukumusabha, nikyo tuno obhuheene bhwo okutuhaana bhino tukumusabha.
\p 
\v 16 Kya wowoosi wuno akumurora omurikyaaye arakora ebhibhi bhino bhitakumwaahura omuutu kure na Taatabhugya kirakeego, amusabhire ku Taatabhugya, na Taatabhugya aramuha obhuhoru. Erabha ego kubhano bhakukora ebhibhi bhiyo. Nawe bhiriho ebhibhi bhino bhikumwaahura omuutu kure na Taatabhugya kirakeego. Enye nitakugaamba amusabhire ku Taatabhugya kubhibhi bhiyo.
\v 17 Okukora ryoryoosi rino ritakungʼarira embere wa Taatabhugya, nikwo okukora ebhibhi. Nawe, hamwe na gayo, bhiriho ebhibhi bhino bhitakumwaahura omuutu kure na Taatabhugya kirakeego.
\p 
\v 18 Tumenyiri kubha abhaana bha Taatabhugya bhatakugeenderera kukora ebhibhi,\f + \fr 5:18 \xt Rora 1 Yohana 3:9.\xt*\f* kwo okubha Omwaana wa Taatabhugya arabhariiha, okubha Seetaani, omubhi wurya atamwe okubhakora ryoryoosi.
\v 19 Tumenyiri kubha etwe ni bhaana bha Taatabhugya, ne ekyaaro kyoosi kirabhaahwa no omubhi wurya, Seetaani, omubhi wurya.
\v 20 Kweeki tumenyiri kubha, Omwaana wa Taatabhugya amariri kuuza, na atuheeri amangʼeeni, okubha tumumenye Taatabhugya. Bhoono, tuno obhumwe na Taatabhugya we eheene, kwo okubha tuno obhumwe no Omwaana waaye Yeesu Krisito. Wuno niwe Taatabhugya we eheene no obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego.
\p 
\v 21 Abhaana bhaane abhaseegwa mubhwiikirirya, mwiiriihe mutaaza kuseengera emisaambwa.\f + \fr 5:21 \fk Mutaaza kuseengera emisaambwa\ft , obhugazuro obhuundi bhuratura kubha, \fqa mwiiriihe kure ne ebhigiro bhyoosi bhino bhikugega omweeya gwa Taatabhugya mukoro yaazo.\f*
